{"tid":1082237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）父母中毒雙亡　1歲B女孭百萬人仔巨債被告上法庭","createTime":"2019-03-28T23:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T00:14:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e82c71cd2101f46a22e1de6185c764a9bf6ee204","tid":1082237,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"03月28日(四) 18:18   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCwAh9X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCwAh9X.png&h=204c0154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孫忠死後，他一對女兒需背負百萬人民幣巨債。（互聯網）<br />\n山東威海男子孫忠去年初與妻子雙雙中毒離世，他兩名分別1歲、9歲的女兒，不但一夜間變成孤兒，還要背負兩人遺留下來的巨額債務，被多名債主先後告上法庭。 <br />\n<br />\n孫父透露，兒子與新抱生前在威海、榮成經營農業公司，因通過預付方式促銷，不時需對外借款。兩人身故後，他們陸續收到23份法院傳票，均要求償還債務，合共143萬元（人民幣‧下同‧約170萬港元），法院去年判令他們償還約118萬元（約140萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n負責此案的律師鞏誌艾指出，「父債子償」在國內法律中是可行的，但需要一定條件，就是死者的子女有承繼選產。子女在繼承父母的遺產後，即使他們缺乏勞動能力，或遺產不足清償所有債務，仍有在遺產的限度內償還債務的責任。"},{"pid":"d8dce67211da6c84a6786af2e9d2ab182388c101","tid":1082237,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T23:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4641eb4047cfcfe2fc6373c2e3ba6b493dd45287","tid":1082237,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T23:44:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190328/mobile/bkn-20190328181822011-0328_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190328%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190328181822011-0328_00952_001.html&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HV6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=4bea58ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190328/mobile/bkn-20190328181822011-0328_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4df796d6f435d5af99b063d7dfcb8202a116b5d3","tid":1082237,"uid":50310,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T23:47:35.000Z","msg":"人仔 都仲要估國家？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/to